<h3 id="embracing-happiness-and-optimism">Embracing Happiness and Optimism</h3>

<p>Here‚Äôs where things get really interesting: the revelation that laughter generates ten times more energy than screams. I had to pause the movie here because‚Ä¶ well, <em>gestures broadly at everything</em>. Think about it: we‚Äôve built so many systems around fear ‚Äì of the other, of change, of loss. But what if, like our monster friends, we‚Äôre just wrong about the fundamental math? What if hope, unity, and yes, even joy, are actually more powerful currencies?</p>

