<p>Who would‚Äôve thought that a children‚Äôs movie from 2001 would speak so aptly to today‚Äôs political landscape? Yet here we are, watching a bunch of monsters figure out what we‚Äôre still struggling to learn: systems built on fear are <em>unsustainable</em>, and ethical compromises for the sake of survival lead to moral decay. More importantly, it reminds us that sometimes the most profound truths come packaged in the most unexpected ways.</p>

